data.text: Grateful to be a part of @vcuhealthheart, @vcu_eng, @VCU_BME & @VCUHealth!  💪💛🖤🐏🖤💛💪 #RamStrong

I chose to get the vaccine because I believe in science and public health, for my daughter to be able to return to school and play with friends, for my friends and family, for my clinical research team members and patients, and for my students and community at large.
